Exo (https://github.com/exo-explore/exo) is licensed under GPL-3.0.
loke does NOT link to or include Exo. Exo is an optional, separate
process that communicates with loke exclusively via its REST API.
This architectural boundary ensures loke's Apache 2.0 licence is
not affected by Exo's GPL-3.0 licence. See docs/epics-and-stories.md
(story F8.4) for details on this boundary.
